# GLOBAL VARIABLES
# ======================================================= #
# ------------------------------------------------------- #
# USER/GROUP ID (LinuxServer.io Style)
# ------------------------------------------------------- #
# Set these to match your host user for correct file permissions.
# Find your IDs by running 'id' on your host system.
#
# Example output: uid=1000(bubba) gid=1000(bubba) ...
#   PUID=1000
#   PGID=1000
